<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Instructions</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your CSS styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        }

        .topnav {
            overflow: hidden;
            background-color: #0077be;
        }

            .topnav a {
                float: right;
                display: block;
                color: #f2f2f2;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 14px 16px;
                text-decoration: none;
            }

            .topnav img {
                float: left;
                max-width: 100%;
                max-height: 100%;
                margin-right: 20px;
            }

            .topnav a:hover {
                background-color: #005c99;
                color: white;
            }

            .topnav a.active {
                background-color: #4CAF50;
                color: white;
            }

        .instructions-box {
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            border: 1px solid black;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Navigation -->
        <div class="topnav">
            <img src="your_image_url_here" alt="CDAC Logo">
            <a href="#logoff">Logoff</a>
            <a href="#register">Register</a>
            <a href="#about">About Us</a>
        </div>

        <div style="padding-left:16px">
            <h2>Top Navigation Example</h2>
        </div>

        <!-- Instructions -->
        <div id="instructions">
            <h2>Instructions</h2>

            <div class="instructions-box">
                <p>Please read the following instructions carefully before starting the exam:</p>

                <ul>
                    <li>The exam consists of multiple-choice questions (MCQs).</li>
                    <li>Each question has four options, out of which only one is correct.</li>
                    <li>Select the correct answer by clicking on the corresponding option.</li>
                    <li>You can navigate between questions using the "Next" and "Previous" buttons.</li>
                    <li>The exam has a fixed duration. The remaining time is displayed on the screen.</li>
                    <li>When the time runs out, the exam will be automatically submitted.</li>
                    <li>You can also manually submit the exam at any time by clicking the "Submit" button.</li>
                    <li>Make sure to review your answers before submitting the exam.</li>
                </ul>

                <form action="">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label><input type="checkbox"> I have read and understood the instructions.</label><br />
                    </div>
                    <a href="test" class="button">Start the Exam</a>
                </form>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Add your JavaScript here -->
</body>
</html>
